parameters.name: TRADE_ACTION_DEAL
parameters.description: Place an order for an instant deal with the specified parameters (set a market order)

parameters.name: TRADE_ACTION_PENDING
parameters.description: Place an order for performing a deal at specified conditions (pending order)

parameters.name: TRADE_ACTION_SLTP
parameters.description: Change open position Stop Loss and Take Profit

parameters.name: TRADE_ACTION_MODIFY
parameters.description: Change parameters of the previously placed trading order

parameters.name: TRADE_ACTION_CLOSE_BY
parameters.description: Close a position by an opposite one

parameters.name: ORDER_FILLING_FOK
parameters.description: This execution policy means that an order can be executed only in the specified volume. If the necessary amount of a financial instrument is currently unavailable in the market, the order will not be executed. The desired volume can be made up of several available offers.

parameters.name: ORDER_FILLING_IOC
parameters.description: An agreement to execute a deal at the maximum volume available in the market within the volume specified in the order. If the request cannot be filled completely, an order with the available volume will be executed, and the remaining volume will be canceled.

parameters.name: ORDER_FILLING_RETURN
parameters.description:
This policy is used only for market (ORDER_TYPE_BUY and ORDER_TYPE_SELL), limit and stop limit orders (ORDER_TYPE_BUY_LIMIT, ORDER_TYPE_SELL_LIMIT, ORDER_TYPE_BUY_STOP_LIMIT and ORDER_TYPE_SELL_STOP_LIMIT) and only for the symbols with Market or Exchange execution modes. If filled partially, a market or limit order with the remaining volume is not canceled, and is processed further.
During activation of the ORDER_TYPE_BUY_STOP_LIMIT and ORDER_TYPE_SELL_STOP_LIMIT orders, an appropriate limit order ORDER_TYPE_BUY_LIMIT/ORDER_TYPE_SELL_LIMIT with the ORDER_FILLING_RETURN type is created.

parameters.name: ORDER_TIME_GTC
parameters.description: The order stays in the queue until it is manually canceled

parameters.name: ORDER_TIME_DAY
parameters.description: The order is active only during the current trading day

parameters.name: ORDER_TIME_SPECIFIED
parameters.description: The order is active until the specified date

parameters.name: ORDER_TIME_SPECIFIED_DAY
parameters.description: The order is active until 23:59:59 of the specified day. If this time appears to be out of a trading session, the expiration is processed at the nearest trading time.

parameters.name: action
parameters.description: Trading operation type. The value can be one of the values of the TRADE_REQUEST_ACTIONS enumeration

parameters.name: magic
parameters.description: EA ID. Allows arranging the analytical handling of trading orders. Each EA can set a unique ID when sending a trading request

parameters.name: order
parameters.description: Order ticket. Required for modifying pending orders

parameters.name: symbol
parameters.description: The name of the trading instrument, for which the order is placed. Not required when modifying orders and closing positions

parameters.name: volume
parameters.description: Requested volume of a deal in lots. A real volume when making a deal depends on an order execution type.

parameters.name: price
parameters.description: Price at which an order should be executed. The price is not set in case of market orders for instruments of the "Market Execution" (SYMBOL_TRADE_EXECUTION_MARKET) type having the TRADE_ACTION_DEAL type

parameters.name: stoplimit
parameters.description: A price a pending Limit order is set at when the price reaches the 'price' value (this condition is mandatory). The pending order is not passed to the trading system until that moment

parameters.name: sl
parameters.description: A price a Stop Loss order is activated at when the price moves in an unfavorable direction

parameters.name: tp
parameters.description: A price a Take Profit order is activated at when the price moves in a favorable direction

parameters.name: deviation
parameters.description: Maximum acceptable deviation from the requested price, specified in points

parameters.name: type
parameters.description: Order type. The value can be one of the values of the ORDER_TYPE enumeration

parameters.name: type_filling
parameters.description: Order filling type. The value can be one of the ORDER_TYPE_FILLING values

parameters.name: type_time
parameters.description: Order type by expiration. The value can be one of the ORDER_TYPE_TIME values

parameters.name: expiration
parameters.description: Pending order expiration time (for TIME_SPECIFIED type orders)

parameters.name: position
parameters.description: Position ticket. Fill it when changing and closing a position for its clear identification. Usually, it is the same as the ticket of the order that opened the position.

parameters.name: position_by
parameters.description: Opposite position ticket. It is used when closing a position by an opposite one (opened at the same symbol but in the opposite direction).
